705928f-a.text:
Neptune Ave., south side, between Shell Road and West 6th Street. A view of the Oceanic Hotel built in 1829, and subsequently rebuilt at a latter date. It is no longer standing according to the maps of 1929. In 1894 it
was the property of A. Lindermann. (Coney Island).
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
